    <content>&lt;h2&gt;Tips for Deeper Meditation&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Visualize:&lt;/strong&gt; Picture the scene in your mind&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Use Scripture:&lt;/strong&gt; Read the passage before each decade&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Use sacred art:&lt;/strong&gt; Look at an image of the mystery&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Focus on one word:&lt;/strong&gt; e.g., &quot;Jesus&quot; or &quot;grace&quot;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;When distracted:&lt;/strong&gt; Gently refocus and continue&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</content>
